Package: bebznet-suite
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Depends: docker.io, docker-compose
Description: Complete Docker networking suite
 Docker suite for networking with integrated services:
 .
 - Pi-hole (DNS filtering & ad blocking)
 - Nginx (Reverse proxy & load balancer)
 - WireGuard (VPN server)
 - Uptime Kuma (Monitoring & alerts)
 - Portainer (Docker container management)
 - CrowdSec (Intrusion detection & prevention)
 - Samba (File sharing)
 - FileBrowser (Web file manager)
